name: Purpose Canadian Financial Income Fund
longDescription: The fund seeks to provide shareholders with (i) long-term capital appreciation through investment in a portfolio of Canadian Banks (defined below) (up to 70% on an equal weighted basis) and Canadian Insurance Companies (defined below) (up to 30% on an equal weighted basis) and (ii) monthly distributions.To achieve its investment objectives, the fund will invest primarily in equity securities of Canadian Banks (up to 70% on an equal weighted basis) and to a lesser extent Canadian Insurance Companies (up to 30% on an equal weighted basis). portfolio of Canadian Banks (defined below) (up to 70% on an equal weighted basis) and CanadianInsurance Companies (defined below) (up to 30% on an equal weighted basis) and (ii) monthlydistributions.
